      "title": "Ceylon Indian Oil Company also reduces the price",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ceylon Indian Oil Company (IOC) has also reduced its fuel prices compared to the Ceylon Petroleum Corporation's reduction in fuel prices.",
        "Accordingly, the company has decided to sell a liter of octane 92 petrol at 450 rupees, a liter of octane 95 petrol at 540 rupees, a liter of auto diesel at 440 rupees and a liter of super diesel at 510 rupees."
      ],
